  schema:name "Black Hole" ;
  schema:description "A black hole is a region of [spacetime](../../../terms/spacetime.md) enclosed by an [event horizon](./event-horizon.md), from which no signal -- not even [light](../../../terms/light.md) -- can escape to an outside observer." ;
